{"tid":2038150,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(支那)政協通過政治決議　包括一致贊成及支持建立港區國安法","createTime":"2020-05-27T11:27:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T17:13:54.000Z","uid":18245,"like":96,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"ea6f227050559696a204e73bc57fcc82414228b1","tid":2038150,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T11:27:01.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】全國政協十三屆三次會議在北京閉幕。<br />\n<br />\n政協閉幕在人民大會堂舉行，大會通過政協常委會工作報告，及由李斌擔任原本港澳辦主任夏寶龍兼任的政協委員會秘書長職務。<br />\n<br />\n另外以2039票贊成、一票反對，通過政治決議，決議提到全國政協一致贊成並支持建立港區國安法，全面貫徹一國兩制，高度支持維護國家安全及支持行政長官依法施政。<br />\n<br />\n政協主席汪洋發表講話提出，政協要提高履職能力、增強工作實效。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=392430\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D392430&d=YPabaHIeuUhgFn7y0hV32YVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=cdd2ac72\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D392430&h=af60648f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=392430</a>"},{"pid":"1e5d6084934cd64855080c33b1f4d290ea0e3336","tid":2038150,"uid":198278,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T11:27:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85b6a531edfb78e15d3a9ba1c909268e9d008982","tid":2038150,"uid":2843,"like":8,"dislike":9,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T11:28:15.000Z","msg":"反對！？誠哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b756ecefdd31f47f5a03cc1921c47c5ceccda577","tid":2038150,"uid":72145,"like":39,"dislike":3,"score":36,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T11:28:27.000Z","msg":"投反對個一票嘅會唔會被消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa99a78743087872cc3f26f8aa904c1c6094897","tid":2038150,"ui